OL,5,     GWhen Bob becomes a handyman in
OL,6,     Gthe quiet village of Chipping
OL,7,     GSodbury, he soon finds all his
OL,8,     Gcustomers are women. Their
OL,9,     Gendless "jobs" keep him busy and
OL,10,     Gleave Bob wondering how he'll
OL,11,     Gkeep up!
